Meaghan Hudson, 25, said she was suffering from multiple myeloma .
She sent text messages in December 2013 saying she had terminal cancer .
Friends rushed to support her, even shaving their heads in solidarity .
They shaved their heads and got matching tattoos of an inspirational song lyric .
Meaghan's sister, Chelsey Whild, said: 'Little stuff, like the fact that her hair grew back pretty thick, usually with cancer patients it doesn't'